<h3 id="sitewide-enhancements">Sitewide enhancements</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Added the ability for opportunity creators to limit their opportunities to a specific agency or department.</li>
  <li>Added a new filter for applicants to search by department.</li>
  <li>Added new filters for pay grade and time-commitment to improve search and to include detail opportunities.</li>
  <li>Launched new functionality to automatically join users to a closed community if they meet the pre-requisites.</li>
  <li>Enhanced the ability to post a detail on the site including additional fields for requirements and how to apply.</li>
</ul>
